      "text": "新康定情歌",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 21.13,
      "time_str": "00:21.13",
      "text": "裁一朵溜溜的白云，",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 26.02,
      "time_str": "00:26.02",
      "text": "给你做一件梦的衣裳，",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 31.76,
      "time_str": "00:31.76",
      "text": "骑上溜溜的马儿，",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 36.58,
      "time_str": "00:36.58",
      "text": "踏着歌声寻找你的芳香。",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 43.25,
      "time_str": "00:43.25",
      "text": "山上那溜溜的月亮，",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 48.46,
      "time_str": "00:48.46",
      "text": "就像你害羞的脸庞，",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
